<body>

The Android robot mascot has a distinctive glass-like appearance with a glossy shader. The specific shader used is often referred to as a "glass" or "plastic" shader, with the following characteristics:
Specular: High glossiness with a sharp specular highlight
Reflectivity: Moderate to high reflectivity, with a slight fade-off towards the edges
Transparency: Partial transparency, with a subtle gradient effect
Color: A bright, electric green color (#A4C639)
This shader gives the Android robot its iconic, futuristic look.
